      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KIARNI PHOENIX (1) was sent out big odds last time where he settled just off the lead but loomed up and ran on to score by 2.5 lengths over 450, at Maitland (25.05). Solid record here winning five races. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can make it two on the bounce. SASSY SUPREME (8) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (30.07) behind Smooth White at The Gardens. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. LIGHTNING HUNTER (5) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at The Gardens over 600m (35.08). Can do much better this time. JUST SAVAGE (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
